text: Aquí ("Here") is the first studio album by Mexican singer-songwriter Julieta Venegas. It was released on March 24, 1997. It was well received by the public. The two singles released were "De Mis Pasos" and "Cómo Sé". ==Track listing== All songs were written by Venegas. ==Singles== *De Mis Pasos *Cómo Sé ==Awards== *MTV Video Music Awards Year Title Result 1998 Best Female Performance by "Cómo Sé" Won Category:1997 albums Category:Julieta Venegas albums Category:Spanish-language albums
title: Aquí
